courses.learning_outcomes:
Upon completion of this course, students will be able to:
1. Converse on simple daily topics;
2. Understand the differences between Hokkinese/ Southern Min, Cantonese and Putonghua in terms of consonants, vowels, tones, vocabulary and grammar;
3. Recite selected ancient and modern poems in Hokkinese/ Southern Min;
4. Recite the lyrics of selected modern songs in Hokkinese/ Southern Min;
5. Understand Putonghua with a Hokkinese/ Southern Min accent better.

完成本科目後，學生將能夠：
1. 掌握簡單的日常會話；
2. 了解福建話、廣東話和普通話在聲母、韻母、聲調、詞彙和語法方面的差異；
3. 用福建話朗誦十餘首古代與現代詩；
4. 用福建話朗誦十餘首現代歌曲的歌詞；
5. 更好地聽懂帶有福建話口音的普通話。
